# AmazonAssist AI – RAG-Powered E-Commerce Customer Support Assistant

## Project Overview

AmazonAssist AI is an intelligent e-commerce customer support chatbot developed using Python, Streamlit, FAISS, and Google's Gemini AI.

The chatbot helps customers with product recommendations, order tracking, refund policies, coupons, and general support queries through a conversational interface.

The project combines Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG), Vector Search, and Generative AI to provide accurate and context-aware responses.

---

## Problem Statement

Customers often have questions regarding:

* Product recommendations
* Order tracking
* Refund and return policies
* Available discounts and coupons
* General support queries

Traditional chatbots provide predefined responses and lack conversational intelligence.

AmazonAssist AI solves this problem by combining AI-powered responses with company data and customer information.

